<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light">
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light">
    <title>iWebix</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #18181b;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 32px 16px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width: 600px; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e4e7; border-radius: 12px;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px 32px 24px 32px; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: #18181b;">
                <span style="color: #8b5cf6;">i</span>Webix
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 0 32px 32px 32px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #18181b;">
                <%= yield %>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 24px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e7; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; color: #71717a;">
                iWebix Studio — письмо отправлено автоматически.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
